data.description: Charming Cape Cod, 2 br's & bath upstairs, 2 br's & bath downstairs. Fresh paint throughout. Kit has Stainless Steel Appliances & new flooring. Breakfast bar between kit & dining room. Kitchen has large walk in pantry. Large family room has a fireplace that has been plumbed for gas or can be used with wood. All hardwood floors throughout. Gas heat installed in 2020 and HVAC (2020),roof (2021) and brand new hot water heater installed 9/2023. Utility room included washer/ dryer and stand up freezer all work but convey as is. Crawl space is encapsulated. Backyard has wood privacy fence. Great location, near ODU, Norfolk Naval Base, major highways, entertainment, shopping & eateries.  SELLER CURRENTLY HAS A VA ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 4.25%.  However, with the VA loan assumption the seller would only be willing to do it if they do a substitution of VA entitlement as they don't want to lose their VA loan benefit.
